column5: Any construction going on in or around the area this year. We are heading up to ONT in 30 days, 12 hours, 48 minutes. Just wondered if we would run into any detours or not
never know around that area--something always seems to be going on.
http://www.511mn.org/default.asp?area=E I-35 from barnum to Duluth is under construction for the last few weeks. good luck
